<section sectnbr = "7B">
<servcat sctnbr = "07" scnbr = "02">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENBP70A7206025" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Air Flow Control Actuator Inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A7206024">Air Flow Control Actuator Removal and Installation</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Set arm to actuator and check if arm operates smoothly when battery voltage is conducted to terminals of actuator connector (1).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<title>
Air flow control actuator operation
</title>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A722013.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "43.365mm" ver = "01" gw = "197" gh = "106"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using ohmmeter, measure resistance between the following terminals of actuator connector (1) at each arm position.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
“3” terminal and “5” terminal
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<spec>
<title>
Air flow control actuator resistance
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "1.456in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.003in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Arm position
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Resistance (25 &#176;C (77 &#176;F))
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
FACE [a]
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Approx. 4.80 kΩ
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
B/L [b]
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Approx. 4.10 kΩ
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
FOOT [c]
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Approx. 3.40 kΩ
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
D/F [d]
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Approx. 2.70 kΩ
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
DFR [e]
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Approx. 2.00 kΩ
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Using ohmmeter, measure resistance between “1” terminal and “3” terminal of actuator connector.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If check result is not as specified, replace air flow control actuator.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Air flow control actuator resistance (Total resistance)
</title>
<ptxt>
6 kΩ at 25 &#176;C (77 &#176;F)
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A722014.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "98.686mm" ver = "01" gw = "172" gh = "263"/>
<callout>
